block se1
    h2.title Extreme Conditions & Environmental Testing
    p.txt Modern vehicles have to stand up to extreme conditions - whether that's the rigours of a frozen road or a hot, humid sub-continental environment. To thoroughly test these conditions, you need a device that can stand up to the same challenges. 

block se2
    h2.title Challenge
    p.txt Not all devices are able to survive in harsh conditions - whether they're simply not built-rugged from the start or have to be put in a case to prevent damage. High-humidity, low temperatures, searing heat - each has its challenges, not to mention risk of drops, knocks or damage in the laboratory. 

block se3
    h2.title Solution
    p.txt Getac is the device of choice for several OEM's to take out into the field, connect with measurement devices and perform as a data acquisition device. They are designed to work in harsh and extreme ambient temperatures, endure high levels of vibration - ensuring there is no costly disruption, device replacement or a need to repeat the test. 


block se4
