    p.txt Our compact, rugged-devices have a number of features that make them perfectly suited to any environment: 


    ol.list 
        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Built-rugged construction permeates every level of our devices.
        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Fast, powerful processors enable rapid working and calculation for the most precise data. 
        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> High ease-of-use and device familiarity ensures seamlessly operability by all members of your team. 
        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> A range of configurations and accessories means our devices can be modulated to suit any task or environment.
        

